==English==

===Etymology===
See [[Flemish]] and [[bond]]

===Noun phrase===
'''[[Flemish]] [[bond]]'''
# In [[bricklaying]], an arrangement of bricks such that each [[course]] consists of [[alternate]] bricks having their [[short]] sides ([[header]]s) and [[long]] sides ([[stretcher]]s) facing outwards, with alternate courses being [[offset]].

